Tiger Claw (Boost)
Level: Swordsage 1, Warblade 1
Prerequisite: One Tiger Claw maneuver
Initiation Action: 1 swift action
Range: Personal
Target: You
Duration: Instantaneous

You can make a Strength based Taunt check (instead of a Jump check) as a swift action and move the distance determined if you succeed your check result. You must have line of sight to where you are leaping.
